| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-0584 — Recovery Inhibition (qilin)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 8625e751-37f0-5b86-a9dd-5a752ffc6e2b"
